description: Ideally located overlooking the Medal of Honor Park, this fully gut-renovated parlor level one bedroom home offers the perfect combination of historic charm & modern updates. The desirable open concept floor plan features a chef's kitchen with custom cabinetry, natural stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, beverage station with built-in fridge & an oversized island with room for 3 barstools. The living space features high ceilings & oversized windows complete with beautiful park views. The open layout flows effortlessly into the kitchen, perfect for entertaining. Down the hall is the bedroom featuring custom built closets and spacious bathroom with glass shower, built-ins for storage & full size w/d. Access your parking space directly from the mudroom with an oversized common yard fit for any season. Additional storage included. Just steps from Southie's best restaurants & shops, M Street Beach, Stop & Shop, public transportation, etc. This one truly checks every box.
